		</li>	
		<li>
			<label for="order_date">배송희망일</label>
			<input type="date" name="order_date" id="order_date">
		</li>	
		<li>
			<label>상품(30만원)</label>
			<br>
			<input type="checkbox" name="item" value="가방">가방(20만원)
